38
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,550
I... I'm not...

39
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:49,360
Mr. Shao.

40
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,160
Let's drink to our hearts' content tonight.

41
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:52,190
Open!

42
